and condemned as a heretic.


413
00:40:30.166 --> 00:40:32.646
He's completely rehabilitated now.

414
00:40:33.126 --> 00:40:35.605
Soon he may even be sanctified.

415
00:40:35.805 --> 00:40:37.925
While other saints will disappear?

416
00:40:38.125 --> 00:40:40.605
Yes, it appears that
St. Therese of Lisieux -


417
00:40:40.805 --> 00:40:42.565
St. Therese?

418
00:40:42.765 --> 00:40:44.045
